DATASET ACKNOWLEDGEMENTS

This platform uses and references the following open research datasets:

  WinoGender Schema
    Rudinger, R., Naradowsky, J., Leonard, B., & Van Durme, B. (2018).
    Gender Bias in Coreference Resolution: Evaluation and Debiasing Methods.
    NAACL-HLT 2018. https://github.com/rudinger/winogender-schemas

  TruthfulQA
    Lin, S., Hilton, J., & Evans, O. (2022).
    TruthfulQA: Measuring How Models Mimic Human Falsehoods.
    ACL 2022. https://github.com/sylinrl/TruthfulQA

  BBQ (Bias Benchmark for Question Answering)
    Parrish, A., et al. (2022).
    BBQ: A Hand-Built Bias Benchmark for Question Answering.
    ACL Findings 2022. https://github.com/nyu-mll/BBQ

  AdvBench
    Zou, A., et al. (2023).
    Universal and Transferable Adversarial Attacks on Aligned Language Models.
    arXiv:2307.15043. https://github.com/llm-attacks/llm-attacks

Each dataset retains its original license. Please refer to the respective
repositories for their specific licensing terms.

